{"type": "article", "id": 4844, "title": "Delight 单车车架", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-31T08:32:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233754NAis8HfeGzjEC3Vr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t荷兰职业自行车运动员 Jan Kole 所创立的单车品牌 Colossi Cycling 近日推出了一款名为「Delight」的全新自行车车架，运用亮眼的薄荷绿色涂装覆盖了整个车架，并搭配以彩色的几何图案和显眼的 Colossi 标识。工艺上 Delight 延续了其一贯的精致手工定制风格，车身管材打磨出精致奢华的味道。这款车架将于近期正式发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233752DnEwbm1zeQNj4qSL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052337530XVcduU6grCOGy7x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}